From 5a066b9db00c1ebb331727bd4330e551d636e88d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: regksem <regksem@tuta.io>
Date: Fri, 19 Jun 2026 18:23:15 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Add configurable forwarding mode (legacy, BungeeGuard,
 Velocity modern)

Adds a dedicated xwaterfall.yml config exposing forwarding_mode +
forwarding_secret, selecting how player information is forwarded to backend
servers when ip_forward is enabled in config.yml:

- BUNGEECORD_LEGACY (default): unchanged classic BungeeCord forwarding.
- BUNGEEGUARD: appends the shared secret as a bungeeguard-token property.
- VELOCITY_MODERN: answers the velocity:player_info login plugin request
  with HMAC-SHA256 signed forwarding data (keyless v1).

xwaterfall.yml is shipped as a commented default resource and read strictly
read-only (XWaterfallConfig) so comments are preserved across restarts and
upgrades; missing keys fall back to code defaults.

